  <brief_title>Changing Diabetes® World Tour</brief_title>
  <official_title>Changing Diabetes® World Tour a Study on the Association of Risk Factors and the Presence of Undiagnosed Diabetes in the Middle East, Northern Africa and Europe</official_title>
  <sponsors>
