  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in the Middle East, Northern Africa and Europe. The aim of this study
      is to contribute to the design of a simple screening strategy for countries in scope, by
      exploring the association between risk factors and undiagnosed diabetes in a screening study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
